    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1944-02-15T10:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1944-02-15T10:00:00-05:00" n="980"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d980">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.0011 LCC/16: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Winant</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-02-15T16:00:00+01:00"
                            >February 15, 1944—4 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received 12 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1264. Sir Orme Sargent states that instructions along the lines of paragraph 7 of
                    his letter of February 11 are being sent to the British Ambassador, Moscow. He
                    assumed that the American Ambassador will receive similar instructions from the
                        Department<note n="13" xml:id="d980fn13">On February 16, 1944, the
                        Department notified Ambassador Winant in telegram 1176, 8 p.m., as follows:
                        “Harriman instructed.” (740.0011 LCC/16) Ambassador Harriman’s instructions
                        were sent in telegram 312, February 16, to Moscow (740.0011 LCC/16a).</note>
                    (this refers to the Department’s 1120, February 14, 2 p.m.).</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Winant</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
